	<div id="content" class="hfeed">
	<article class="post-6094 post type-post status-publish hentry category-deeper-dive tag-automobiles tag-chrysler-group-llc tag-dodd-frank-wall-street-reform-and-consumer-protection-act-2010 tag-emergency-economic-stabilization-act-2008 tag-ford-motor-co tag-general-motors tag-goolsbee-austan-d tag-gross-domestic-product tag-gross-national-product-gnp tag-krueger-alan-b tag-obama-barack tag-presidential-election-of-2016 tag-recession-and-depression tag-unemployment tag-united-states tag-united-states-economy tag-university-of-chicago tag-white-house-council-of-economic-advisers per-goolsbee-austan-d per-krueger-alan-b per-obama-barack des-automobiles des-dodd-frank-wall-street-reform-and-consumer-protection-act-2010 des-emergency-economic-stabilization-act-2008 des-gross-domestic-product des-gross-national-product-gnp des-presidential-election-of-2016 des-recession-and-depression des-unemployment des-united-states-economy org-chrysler-group-llc org-ford-motor-co org-general-motors org-university-of-chicago org-white-house-council-of-economic-advisers geo-united-states news_keywords-2016-presidential-election news_keywords-alan-b-krueger news_keywords-austan-d-goolsbee news_keywords-barack-obama news_keywords-cars news_keywords-chrysler-group news_keywords-council-of-economic-advisers news_keywords-dodd-frank news_keywords-gdp news_keywords-gm news_keywords-gnp news_keywords-recession-and-depression news_keywords-tarp news_keywords-unemployment news_keywords-university-of-chicago news_keywords-us news_keywords-us-economy" id="post-6094">
	<header class="postHeader">
